      • valueOf

        public static HttpStatus valueOf​(int code)
        Resolves HttpStatus from given status code.

        If given code is a standardized status, a cached HttpStatus is returned. Otherwise, a new instance is returned.

        Parameters:
        code - Code to resolve.
        Returns:
        Resolved or new HttpStatus.
